lyrics:
Guclu olmayi istedik rabbim sorunlari cozmem icin beni yasama bagladi

[Verse]
Allah, the One who guides us on our way
In every moment, in every part of the day
His love and mercy, forever shining bright
He listens to our prayers, both day and night

[Chorus]
Allah, oh Allah, we seek Your love
You're the One we adore, the Mighty above
Guide us through darkness, and show us the light
Allah, oh Allah, be with us day and night
